SystemServer auto test to ensure the performance and stability of SystemServer process.

This should be built separately for test purpose.


WHAT IT DOES?
=============
MediaTekSystemServerTestCases contains test cases for bootup time and the availability
of critical system services.


HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
Use AOPS mmm command with this folder path to build the apk file.


HOW TO USE IT?
==============

Dev Tools -> Instrument -> System Server Test Case

or

adb shell am instrument -w com.mediatek.SystemServer.test/android.test.InstrumentationTestRunner


